## Task BP-002: Add Pack Validation

Create:

```text
src/engine/benchmarks/shared/validateBenchmarkPack.ts
```

Validation must check:
- required fields exist
- scenario IDs unique
- rank IDs unique
- aliases not duplicated
- thresholds reference existing scenarios
- thresholds reference existing ranks
- universal categories valid
- platforms valid
- threshold scores are numbers

Acceptance:
- invalid pack returns clear error
- valid sample pack passes
- tests cover invalid references

